    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Traveling-Light"><a href="#Traveling-Light" class="headerlink" title="Traveling Light"></a>Traveling Light</h2><p>Joel Hanson、Sara Groves</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=674524201&bvid=BV1ZU4y1E7Pg&cid=381874414&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="If-I-Die-Young"><a href="#If-I-Die-Young" class="headerlink" title="If I Die Young"></a>If I Die Young</h2><p>Kimberly Perry</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=860423434&bvid=BV1gG4y1d7Mu&cid=901581204&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="Waiting-For-Love"><a href="#Waiting-For-Love" class="headerlink" title="Waiting For Love"></a>Waiting For Love</h2><p>Avicii </p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=202139193&bvid=BV1Eh411X7eM&cid=236417064&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="Hymn-For-The-Weekend"><a href="#Hymn-For-The-Weekend" class="headerlink" title="Hymn For The Weekend"></a>Hymn For The Weekend</h2><p>Alan Walker</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=5166654&bvid=BV1rs411v7Kx&cid=8396556&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="Tennis-Elbow"><a href="#Tennis-Elbow" class="headerlink" title="Tennis Elbow"></a>Tennis Elbow</h2><p>Sky Sailing</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=994619920&bvid=BV1Zs4y12762&cid=1082737272&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="It’s-My-Life"><a href="#It’s-My-Life" class="headerlink" title="It’s My Life"></a>It’s My Life</h2><p>Bon Jovi </p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=997229277&bvid=BV1Vs4y1y7TP&cid=1160307388&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="Centuries"><a href="#Centuries" class="headerlink" title="Centuries"></a>Centuries</h2><p>Fall Out Boy</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=454341170&bvid=BV1m5411k7ua&cid=1420401989&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="I-Am-You"><a href="#I-Am-You" class="headerlink" title="I Am You"></a>I Am You</h2><p>Kim Taylor</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=481223288&bvid=BV1iT411C7jW&cid=989948176&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="This-Is-The-Life"><a href="#This-Is-The-Life" class="headerlink" title="This Is The Life"></a>This Is The Life</h2><p>Angie Miller</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=599221846&bvid=BV1AB4y1k7RT&cid=796256639&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h2 id="We-Can’t-Stop"><a href="#We-Can’t-Stop" class="headerlink" title="We Can’t Stop"></a>We Can’t Stop</h2><p>Boyce Avenue &amp; Bea Miller</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=21522159&bvid=BV1VW411T7GY&cid=35430102&p=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" width="100%" height="500" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>]]></content>
    
    
